TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Check if source row exist in target table a) if present then compare the column values of source and target. If there is a difference then set CHANGE_FLAG = 1 to denote it as changed record else CHANGE_FLAG = 0 b) If not present then set NEW_FLAG=1 to denote as new record.

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(Tgt_RCOBJ_ID) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_RCOBJ_TYP_CD ) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_CORP_OWNR_ID) AND ( Tgt_RCOBJ_CRTE_DT!=var_RCOBJ_CRTE_DT or Tgt_RCOBJ_CRTE_USR_ID!=var_RCOBJ_CRTE_USR_ID or RTRIM(LTRIM(Tgt_RCOBJ_RSN_CD))!=RTRIM(LTRIM(var_RCOBJ_RSN_CD)) or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_ORGR_CD!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_ORGR_CD or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_RSN_CD!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_RSN_CD or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_RSLTN_CD!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_RSLTN_CD or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_ADMN_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_ADMN_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_BASE_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_BASE_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_PRFRM_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_PRFRM_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_FRMLY_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_FRMLY_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_CNPRC_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_CNPRC_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_DS_PRCPT_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_DS_PRCPT_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_RSL_ADMN_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_RSL_ADMN_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_RSL_BASE_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_RSL_BASE_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_RSL_PRFRM_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_RSL_PRFRM_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_RSL_FRMLY_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_RSL_FRMLY_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_RSL_CNPRC_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_RSL_CNPRC_IN or Tgt_RCOBJ_RSL_PRCPT_IN!=Src_RCOBJ_RSL_PRCPT_IN or IIF(ISNULL(RTRIM(LTRIM(Tgt_RCOBJ_CMNT_TX))),'NA',RTRIM(LTRIM(Tgt_RCOBJ_CMNT_TX))) != IIF(ISNULL(RTRIM(LTRIM(Src_RCOBJ_CMNT_TX))),'NA',RTRIM(LTRIM(Src_RCOBJ_CMNT_TX)))), 1, 0 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Changed_Flag
